body:
The desc property, in the node_config example, is missing an end quote
{
  "composer": {
    "wallet": {
      "type": "composer-wallet-redis",
      "desc": "Uses a local redis instance,
...

should be 

{
  "composer": {
    "wallet": {
      "type": "composer-wallet-redis",
      **"desc": "Uses a local redis instance",**
...

https://github.com/hyperledger/composer/issues/1535

Remove the HLFv0.6 configuration and files from the fabric-dev-servers package.
@davidkel informs me it wasn't working anyway, and we're removing all code related to Hyperledger Fabric v0.6 support.
